data.description: GREAT PRICE!!  GREAT HOUSE!! GREAT LOCATION!! This home features beautiful engineered wood floors in the Dining, Kitchen, Living Room and Primary Bedroom.  Granite counters in the Kitchen and Baths. The large Living Room has a soaring 12’ Cathedral Ceiling and Brick Wood Burning Fireplace!! Plenty of storage with large walk-in closets in 3 of the bedrooms and a spacious laundry room.  The 4th bedroom has its own private entrance and would make a great bonus room or second living area.  Conveniently located minutes to I-10 and I-12.  PREFERRED FLOOD ZONE!
